Even before the Netscape deal, America Online was moving to provide some electronic commerce software and services.This new software, which now will be combined with Netscape's online store services, will be available for companies to use both on America Online and on the Internet.America Online Inc. wants to become the ``next Microsoft'' in two promising information-age fields where Microsoft Corp. is just another company _ the Internet media business and electronic commerce.Nearly lost in the complexity of America Online's deal to buy Netscape Communication Corp. is America Online's announcement that it will enter an entirely new market: working behind the computer screen to help companies open and operate online stores.